# Operation name

## Preconditions and authority

Name authoritative sources, identity, capability, granted authority, approval,
target, environment, duration, and revocation.

## Procedure and bounded evidence

List exact steps. Each command reports the invariant, target, recovery hint,
bounded excerpt/detail path, and postcondition.

## Rollback, escalation, and cleanup

Name the last known good state, reversal, escalation owner, cleanup proof,
limitations, and explicit non-claims.
